  "title": "Photographer",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking a talented and experienced photographer to join our creative team. In this role, you will be responsible for capturing compelling, high-quality images at a variety of live events, including corporate functions, conferences, government events, networking events, and more. You’ll play a key part in telling the story of each event through powerful and engaging imagery.<br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Capture professional, high-resolution photographs at live events with attention to lighting, composition, and storytelling.</li><li>Taking individual/class photos of kindergarten.</li><li>Collaborate with clients to understand event goals, schedules, and key moments to capture.</li><li>Edit and retouch photos using industry-standard software, ensuring timely delivery of final images.</li><li>Organise and manage image selection, editing workflow, and file delivery.</li><li>Handle ad-hoc tasks to support ongoing projects</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements & Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Proven experience in photography with a strong, diverse portfolio of previous work.</li><li>Proficiency with professional photography gear (DSLR/mirrorless cameras, lenses, lighting).</li><li>Expertise in photo editing software such as Adobe Lightroom and Photoshop.</li><li>Ability to work in dynamic, fast-paced environments and adapt to varying lighting conditions.</li><li>Strong time management skills with the ability to meet tight deadlines.</li><li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Willingness to work<strong> evenings, weekends, and holidays </strong></li></ul><p><strong>Preferred Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Experience with videography is a plus.</li></ul><p><strong>Additional Information</strong></p><ul><li>Familiarity with various photography styles, including candid, posed, and documentary-style.</li><li>This role offers the opportunity to work with a passionate, dynamic team on a variety of exciting projects.</li><li>For <strong>Singaporeans & PR only</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Interested candidates are invited to submit their resume & portfolio with a recent photograph.</strong></p>",
