    "description": "<p><strong>Panorama Photography</strong> is one of the top photography company based in Singapore and is well verse in various areas of photography.</p>\n<p>We have numerous corporate portfolio of events photography and our clients include People Association (we are the official vendor), DBS, UOB, Westcon, Exclusive Network, SPH, Western Union, KAO, Johnson &amp; Johnson, Pirelli and etc. We are also the official photographers of graduation photos and concerts for MindChamps, Maple Bear and Little School House.</p>\n<p>We have a team of professional photographers/videographers with more than 15 years of experience.</p>",
